        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "扈止也止民使不淫放魯昭公十七年郯子來朝叔孫昭子問焉曰少昊氏鳥名官何故也郯子曰吾祖也我知之昔者黄帝氏以雲紀故為雲師而雲名炎帝氏以火紀故為火師而火名共工氏以水紀故為水師而水名太昊氏以龍紀故為龍師而龍名我髙祖少昊摯之立也鳯鳥適至故紀於鳥為鳥師而鳥名自髙陽以來不能紀逺乃紀於近為民師而命以民事則不能故也仲尼聞之見郯子而學之告人曰吾聞之天子失官學在四夷猶信然則古聖人之建官立事必本於學也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 97,
          "end": 117
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "能治其官",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 117,
          "end": 122
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "木正",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-20",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 122,
          "end": 126
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "金正",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-21",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 126,
          "end": 133
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "二子相代為水正",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-22",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 133,
          "end": 138
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "窮桑少昊之號也四子能治其官使不失職濟成少昊之功死皆為民所祀窮桑地在魯北晋頃公十四年魏獻子問於蔡墨曰社稷五祀誰氏之五官也對曰少昊氏有四叔為勾芒蓐收𤣥冥此其三祀也顓頊氏有子曰黎為祝融共工氏有子曰勾龍為后土此其二祀也后土為社稷田正也有烈山氏之子曰柱為稷自夏以上祀之周棄亦為稷自商以來祀之",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-23",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 150
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "為善日不足也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-24",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 150,
          "end": 157
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "二人並耕曰耦式車敬耕者也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-25",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 157,
          "end": 161
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "下車也十室之邑以其必有忠信故下之",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-26",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "甘盤賢臣有道徳者",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-27",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "伏羲畫八卦文王演之為六十四",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-28",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 24,
          "end": 68
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "亹亹勉也其善聲聞無止時也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-29",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 68,
          "end": 79
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "穆穆美也緝熈光明也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-30",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 79,
          "end": 89
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "倬大也雲漢在天其為文章辟猶天子為法度于天下",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-31",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 89,
          "end": 105
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "追琢玉使成文章喻文王為政先以心研精合于禮義然後施之萬民其好而學之如覩金玉然言其政可樂也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-32",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 105,
          "end": 123
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "雝雝和也肅肅敬也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-33",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 123,
          "end": 133
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "性與天合",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-34",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 133,
          "end": 159
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "此文王燕朋友之詩",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-35",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 159,
          "end": 167
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "言質性有文徳",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-36",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 167,
          "end": 223
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "師之尚之父之故曰師尚父",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-37",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 97
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "保謂安守之",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-38",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 97,
          "end": 102
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "傅猶敷也",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-39",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 102,
          "end": 107
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "師傳之教大同也師主於訓導傅即受而述之書序曰召公為保周公為師相成王為左右盖周公復政留為太師",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
